         * 4. Focus management (visible focus indicators, focus trap in modal)
         * 5. WCAG-compliant color contrast
         * 6. Respect for prefers-reduced-motion
         * 7. Form validation with accessible error messages
         * 8. Skip links and landmark regions
         * 9. Alt text placeholders for images
         * 10. Responsive design for all screen sizes
         *
         * ==============================================
         * PERFORMANCE CONSIDERATIONS
         * ==============================================
         *
         * - Intersection Observer for efficient scroll animations
         * - CSS transforms for smooth animations (GPU-accelerated)
         * - Lazy loading ready (add to images when implemented)
         * - Minimal JavaScript - only where necessary
         * - No external dependencies
         *
         * ==============================================
         * CUSTOMIZATION NOTES
         * ==============================================
         *
         * To customize for production:
         *
